==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: endogamic
<hw>endogamic</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>fertilized by pollen
from another flower of the same plant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>of marriage within a class or tribe as required by
custom or law; same as <er>endogamous</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> endogamous, within-group.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Endogamous</ent>⟦br⟧
